      • radiusOnUse

        ImmutableBoundedValue<Double> radiusOnUse()
        Gets the bounded radiusOnUse value of this cloud. The radius is reduced per Entity affected. Once the radius is 0, the cloud dissipates.
        Returns:
        The bounded radius reduced on use value

      • radiusPerTick

        ImmutableBoundedValue<Double> radiusPerTick()
        Gets the bounded radiusPerTick value of this cloud. The radius is reduced per tick (so technically can be set to 0 to have it remain permanent until it's effects have been used up.
        Returns:
        The bounded radius reduction per tick value

      • durationOnUse

        ImmutableBoundedValue<Integer> durationOnUse()
        Gets the bounded durationOnUse value of this cloud. The duration on use is reduced for every time that this cloud applies it's PotionEffects on an Entity.
        Returns:
        The bounded duration on use value

      • applicationDelay

        ImmutableBoundedValue<Integer> applicationDelay()
        Gets the bounded applicationDelay value of this cloud. What this means is the application delay between times of application on an Entity.
        Returns:
        The bounded re-application delay value

      • effects

        ImmutableListValue<PotionEffect> effects()
